quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  33,41,"Ko onon yo …ďen gom…óim…ďe, jantoree Alla jantoore …óuu…óunde"
  33,42,Subhinee Mo bimmbi e kiikii…óe
  33,43,"Ko Kanko woni yurmetee…óo on, -e Malaa'ikaa…ďe Makko …ďen (du'orana on), - fii no O yaltinira on e ni…ďe faade e annoora. O siforii hinnotoo…óo gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  33,44,"Hiwrondiral ma…ď…ďe ngal √Īalnde …ďe hawrata e Makko, ko \"Salaam\" [kisiyee], O maranii …ďe mbarjaari teddundi"
  33,45,"Ko an yo Annabiijo ! Men nulirii ma [fii yo wonu] seedii…óo, e wewlinoowo e jertinoowo"
  33,46,"e noddoowo faade e Alla, duŇčayee Makko; e pitilol jal…ďungol"
  33,47,"Wewlinir gom…óim…ďe …ďen, wonnde no woodani …ďe ka Alla, …ďural mawnungal"
  33,48,"Wata a …óofto heefer…ďe …ďen e naafiqii…ďe …ďen, …óuurno (e) lorra ma…ď…ďe kan, fawo-…óaa e Alla. Sabu Alla yonii ka fawee"
  33,49,"Ko onon yo …ďen gom…óim…ďe ! Si resii rew…ďe gom…óim…ďe …ďen, refti on seerii …ďe ado on meemondirde e ma…ď…ďe, haray alanaa on e ma…ď…ďe, edda mo …ďe eddinotoo. Dakmitiree …ďe [njoo…ďa], seeriron …ďe cergal la…ďaangal"
  33,50,"Ko an yo Annabiijo ! Men daginanii ma suddii…ďe maa …ďen …ďe jonnu-…óaa teŇče mun …ďen, e …ďen [hor…ďe] …ďe jeyru-…óaa √Īaamo maa, e …ďen [dahaa…ďe] …ďe Alla neldu-maa, e jiw…ďe bappa maa, e jiw…ďe yaayiraa…ďe maa, e jiw…ďe kaawu-maa, e jiw…ďe neeniraa…ďe maa, - …ďen feridunoo…ďe e maa, - e suddii…óo gom…óin…óo, si o ye…óii hoore-makko Annabiijo on, si Annabiijo on kadi faandike resugol mo : …óum ko ko heerani maa, gaanin gom…óim…ďe …ďen. Gom…óii Me…óen anndi ko Men farli e ma…ď…ďe kon, e fii suddii…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, e ko …ďe jeytiri √Īaame ma…ď…ďe …óen, fii wata …ďi…óteende wonu e maa…óa. Alla laatike haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  33,51,"Hi…óa nennintina on mo yi…óu-…óaa (nennintinnde) e ma…ď…ďe, …ďa…ótinaa e maa…óa on mo yi…óu-…óaa. E on mo …óa…ď…ďu-…óaa (belagol ka mun) e …ďen …ďe nennitu-…óaa, bakkaaku woo fawaaki ma. Ko …óum …ďuri …ďadaade e ko …ďu…ď…ďinta …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe, hara …ďe sunotaako, …ďe weltora kadi ko okku-…óaa …ďe kon, …ďe fow ma…ď…ďe. Alla no Anndi ko woni e …ďer…óe mon. Alla laatike Anndu…óo, Mu√Ī√Īii…óo"
  33,52,"Rew…ďe …ďen dagitantaako ma …ďaawo […ďee …óoo], wanaa nde wa…ótitirtaa …ďe genndiraa…ďe goo, hay si Ňčari …ďen …óon haawnii ma; si wanaa …ďe jeyru-…óaa √Īaamo maa …ďen. Alla laatike tommbii…óo kala huunde"